{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act22side_level_act22side_st02","storyGroup":"act22side","storySort":15,"storyDependence":"act22side_level_act22side_07_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"FC-ST-2","storyName":"自灰烬之中","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"跟随在苇草身边的塔拉人，大多数决定继续战斗。此时，爱布拉娜与威灵顿公爵正在高速战舰上眺望，深池大军已经做好准备。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act22side/level_act22side_st02","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act22side_st02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":13,"next":15,"characters":["菲舍尔","开斯特公爵","受伤的流民","苇草","维恩","塔拉流民","莫兰","爱布拉娜","威灵顿公爵","维多利亚军官","沃里克伯爵","拉芙希妮"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"Dialog","id":3},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"$darkness02_loop","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......“阿赫茉妮”的间谍身份得以确认，但她安插的情报人员已经全部在掩护下提前撤离。","id":11,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"那名感染者的确是另一条德拉克。她的动向已经在我们的掌控之中，只要得到指令，我的部队会继续追捕。","id":12,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......另外，恕我冒昧，请问在屏风后听取汇报的人，您是头领，还是......公爵阁下？","id":14,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":15},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_726_1#7$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"你很敏锐，上一个能指出这一点的孩子，我已经不记得是在几年前遇见的了。","id":18,"figure":"avg_npc_726_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"抱歉，我只是想享用完这杯红茶。请坐过来吧。","id":19,"figure":"avg_npc_726_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......","id":21,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"不，作为感染者，我站在这里就好。","id":23,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"你来的时候，看到街角那家小剧院了吗？","id":25,"figure":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"是，我看到了......剧院没有开张，也没有可疑的人在附近徘徊。","id":27,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"那是一些自称塔拉人的艺术家建起的剧院，每晚那里都会上演基于塔拉文化创作的剧目。","id":29,"figure":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......需要我去调查他们吗？","id":31,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"不，我很欣赏他们的存在。","id":33,"figure":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"追捕那条德拉克的事，你不用担心，我会交给其他人去做。你带来的情报很有价值，以你的才能，不必把时间消耗在收尾的工作上。","id":34,"figure":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_726_1#7$1","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"我想请你，为我去特定地点监视威灵顿公爵的行动。","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_726_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲舍尔","text":"......是，感谢您的赏识。","id":38,"figure":"avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"开斯特公爵","text":"对了，之前那个问题，你想好答案了吗？","id":40,"figure":"avg_npc_726_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":41},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":42},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":43},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":44},{"type":"Character","id":45},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g1_victoriavillage","screenadapt":"coverall","id":46},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":47},{"type":"PlayMusic","key":"$calm_loop","volume":"0.4","id":48,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":49},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":50},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"受伤的流民","text":"哎，信使小姐，你能把信捎多远？多远都行？","id":52,"figure":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"受伤的流民","text":"那，你能帮忙写信吗？","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"受伤的流民","text":"就写几句话，我只是想跟家里人说一声我还活着......","id":54,"figure":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":55},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":56},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":57},{"type":"Character","id":58},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g1_victoriavillage","screenadapt":"coverall","id":59},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":60},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":61},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":62},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"刚刚那位农户说的，你们应该听到了。这里定时会有商队路过，半小时后就会有一支。","id":64,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"你们跟着商队走，能藏进载具的话，最好。靠近橡林郡的地区，应该是威灵顿公爵直属的领地，他不会容许针对塔拉人的暴行。","id":65,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"错过这次机会的话，会很危险。搜捕队从附近的移动城市赶到这里，以最快的速度，应该不用一小时。","id":66,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......但你们只要能逃出去，之后的生活就不用太担心。那些人想要的是我，跟丢了你们的踪迹之后，他们不会再追的。","id":68,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#4$1","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"呃，等等......所以，风笛说你是什么深池的领袖，不是我听错了？","id":70,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯，如果你们之中还有人想要跟着深池战斗，可以和我一起，继续走。","id":72,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"但深池的身份没有办法成为你们的保护伞。之后的路，或许也会像现在一样......被很多人监视，继续被人追赶。","id":74,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":75},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":76},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":77},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":78},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"受伤的流民","text":"我回来了，嘿。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"受伤的流民","text":"我照着你的话跟她说了，说我跟村里逃出来的人一起，在这边落脚了，然后编了个石高原野上找不到的地名。","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"受伤的流民","text":"......可那个信使看起来人挺好的，要是她是真的信使，不是来查我们动向的人，那我不是害得她白跑一趟？","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......我大部分时间，都过着东躲西藏的生活。像她那样假扮信使的追踪者，我见过许多。","id":84,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"受伤的流民","text":"唉，好吧。以后还要继续这么过。","id":86,"figure":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_242","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"别叹气了，我们抓紧时间分一分手上的物资。","id":88,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔拉流民","text":"你这样受伤了的，就别勉强自己跟着苇草走了。为塔拉人打仗的事，我们帮你。","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_242"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"受伤的流民","text":"哈哈，那我这算不算是，已经为塔拉人打过啦......","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_729_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......苇草，过来过来。","id":93,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"我得跟你说件事。","id":94,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":95},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":96},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","id":97},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.2","id":98},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"200","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":99},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":100},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":101},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":102},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","fadetime":"0.7","id":103},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":104},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"本来我是写在遗书上的，唉，但我活下来了嘛。","id":106,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"嗯。怎么了？","id":108,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":109},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#2$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......一开始，用锄头砸倒那个士兵，害得所有人都得逃跑的人，是我。","id":112,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"那天晚上，我见到当兵的在打人，打图利家的小女儿，就从别人家的墙根抄了一把锄头，摸了过去。","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":115},{"type":"shake","name":"left","power":"2","times":"60","fadetime":"0.4","block":"true","id":116},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":117},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"我是不是抖得厉害？......真对不起，唉。过去这么久了，我还老是梦见那个场景。","id":119,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"女孩才十四岁，尖声尖气的，哭得让人心慌。","id":120,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"我想，天那么黑，也不许点灯，就算这一锄头砸破了头，流了血，样子再怎么惨，我也看不清楚。","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#5$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"我就是......我没想到害了那么多人。","id":123,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"后来我想陪着他们，给所有人想办法安顿下来，自己再离开，算是偿还我犯的错......","id":124,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"可是有的人最后也没能走到落脚的地方。","id":126,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......证件不齐的罪名，是你给自己编的吗？","id":128,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"唉，对不起。","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"一开始通缉令上面没有我，我怕他们起疑心，才特地跟费加尔一块去抢药店......结果又把你也牵扯进来。","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"不要这么说，维恩。我的身份，总有一天会追上我。","id":133,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......塔拉人的悲哀，也总有一天会追上每个人。","id":135,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......好，好，唉。","id":137,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":138},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":139},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":140},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"哎，莫兰，你想不想......","id":142,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"怎么了，维恩？","id":144,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......不，没什么。绳子给我吧，我来捆，你这样带着行李走不远。","id":146,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"呵呵，你是行家。","id":148,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"你也要跟着苇草继续打仗？","id":150,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"嗯。塞尔蒙说，我很有力气，应该可以做不少事。","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......可你在黑的地方就看不见东西，多不方便。","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"而且，那可是打仗啊，要面对的敌人肯定比我们那天晚上见到的更多，更厉害。","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"还有大炮。打仗不是那种被砍一刀流点血的事，不是戏里面演的那样，英雄被打倒，还能爬起来。人会一下子就死掉，死得很难看......","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"......但是我想选这条路。","id":158,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫兰","text":"我想，抓住我生活里难得的选择机会。","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_728_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"商队靠近了。","id":162,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"好，我去和他们交涉，把受伤的人送走。","id":164,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......","id":165,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#2$1","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"......","id":167,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"苇草......我能走吗？","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维恩","text":"现在的我，能离开了吗？","id":170,"figure":"avg_npc_725_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":171},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":172},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":173},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"Character","id":175},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","id":176},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":177},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":179},{"type":"Text","text":"我想，一切都已经准备好了。","id":180},{"type":"Text","text":"只剩下......我的妹妹，她还在外彷徨，但她终究会做出正确的选择。","id":181},{"type":"Dialog","id":182},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":183},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":184},{"type":"Character","id":185},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck","screenadapt":"coverall","id":186},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":187},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.4","id":188,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":189},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":190},{"type":"Text","text":"“加斯特里尔”号高速战舰甲板","id":191},{"type":"Dialog","id":192},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":193},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":194},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"曾经最庞大的移动城市上抽离的一根骸骨，搭载维多利亚军工技术纯粹的结晶，多少人该以登上这艘高速战舰为荣。","id":196,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"纵使放眼整片泰拉大地，我想也不会有能与此媲美的军事机器。","id":197,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"威灵顿公爵","text":"若非如此，它便配不上德拉克麾下传奇将领之名。","id":199,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":200},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"也有许多人一直窥探着它的动向，试图从中揣摩您的立场......","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":202},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"在长达七年的巡游之后，今天该是它靠岸的日子了。","id":203,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":204},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":205},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"威灵顿公爵","text":"我们转向后，有多少信使正在回报讯息的路上？","id":207,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_241","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚军官","text":"除了开斯特公爵，各位公爵都在保持关注，但他们掌控下的任何一支军队都已经来不及干预。","id":209,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚军官","text":"橡林郡已经停止行驶，做好接驳准备。虽然这是本舰七年来首次靠近一座移动城市，但停留过程中，并无过多资源补给和机械维护需求。","id":210,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚军官","text":"伯爵表示，届时会亲自前往港口迎接您。","id":211,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":212},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":213},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"威灵顿公爵","text":"那些踟蹰不前的阿斯兰附庸，恐怕到这艘舰船径直驶向橡林郡的时刻才会发现，这座城市究竟权属归谁。","id":215,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":216},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"而这里将再次升起怎样的火焰，他们还一无所知。","id":217,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"深池的军队，那些渴望从不公中解脱的塔拉人，已经从维多利亚各处赶来。","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我的谋臣......她做得很不错。","id":219,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":220},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":221},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"威灵顿公爵","text":"我的城市，是否停在了我期望的地点？","id":223,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_241","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚军官","text":"是。受限于地形与安全因素，这就是城市航道上最靠近废城遗迹的位置。","id":225,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"威灵顿公爵","text":"您怎么看，爱布拉娜殿下？在前来的路上，您造访过那处遗址。","id":227,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我想这样就够了。无论塔拉文化的复兴者将多少想象寄托在盖尔王的王城上，那终究只是一处衰朽的废墟。","id":229,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"届时那些浪漫的梦想家只需要透过原野的晨雾，朝它的方向投去一瞥，知道它曾经矗立在山丘上而如今已经被天灾损毁，就够了。","id":230,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"威灵顿公爵","text":"我听说，塔拉王朝覆灭、德拉克族裔出逃后，阿斯兰们放任那座石城空置，直到它在天灾中坍塌，几乎被塔拉人遗忘。","id":232,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"那古旧王朝的残余......原本也十分无趣。","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"维多利亚的君主分封的盖尔王头衔，不过是仆臣的美称。要是留有王冠，我就要将它熔毁；要是尚有王座，我就要将它一把火烧成灰烬。","id":235,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"不过，那里却连这些都不剩了。","id":236,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"威灵顿公爵","text":"因此那位年轻的沃里克，从盖尔王的传说开始找回塔拉的历史，不是坏事。","id":238,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"您说的是那位“颂古者”沃里克，“北方战线的沃里克”？......啊，您认识他？","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":241},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"威灵顿公爵","text":"我曾向他的宴会派出使者。这艘战舰的巡游正是从那时开始。","id":242,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":243},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"您一向高瞻远瞩。","id":244,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"威灵顿公爵","text":"这不算多么长久的等待。","id":246,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"威灵顿公爵","text":"橡林郡......您想去看看这座城市吗？","id":248,"figure":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"当然。我很好奇，在那场大火后，它被重塑成了什么模样。","id":250,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_652_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"毕竟，它曾经是我的家乡。","id":252,"figure":"avg_npc_722_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":253},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":254},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":256},{"type":"Character","id":257},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","id":258},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":259},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$burningloop1","volume":"0.6","loop":"true","channel":"kfire","id":260},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":261},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":262},{"type":"Text","text":"我握着姐姐的长枪，站在走廊上等了一会儿。","id":263},{"type":"Text","text":"府邸里的每个人都沉默地低着头，刻意忙碌着，一旦看到我就移开视线。","id":264},{"type":"Text","text":"老师的身体一直不好，晚上冒着风雪从宴会回来后就没有离开过自己的房间。戴莉医生为他准备了甜酒，却没有按时来取走空杯。","id":265},{"type":"Text","text":"门缝中传出细小的木头爆裂声。雪夜的炉火应该很温暖，此刻火焰平静燃烧的声音却令我牙齿打战。","id":266},{"type":"Text","text":"我还是推开了门。","id":267},{"type":"Dialog","id":268},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$rebel_intro","key":"$rebel_loop","volume":"0.4","id":269,"musicid":3},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_open_door","volume":"1","id":270},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0.8","g":"0.8","b":"0.8","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":272},{"type":"Image","image":"34_i11","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":273},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"0","xTo":"230","yTo":"-50","xScaleFrom":"1.6","yScaleFrom":"1.4","xScaleTo":"1.4","yScaleTo":"1.4","duration":"0.5","block":"false","id":274},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":275},{"type":"soundvolume","channel":"kfire","volume":"1","fadetime":"4","id":276},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沃里克伯爵","text":"......既然你已经说服所有人背叛了我......那这杯甜酒，我为什么不喝呢？","id":279},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我以为，您会想知道自己哪里有过失，才导致您的仆从们求助于我。","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沃里克伯爵","text":"咳咳......这不重要，爱布拉娜......","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沃里克伯爵","text":"重要的是，你能使他们，一直信你吗？","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"啊，当然。","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"您也不问，为什么我愿意答应他们。","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沃里克伯爵","text":"咳......你知道，我死后，这座城市会发生什么吗？","id":285},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"230","yFrom":"-50","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.4","yScaleFrom":"1.4","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"30","block":"false","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"贵族间的力量会失衡，菲利普伯爵在议会上的发言不会再有人反对，但为了得到斯塔福德公爵的重视，那两位年轻的男爵会在暗中动手。","id":287},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"与此同时，刚刚找回姓名的塔拉人会失去他们的领袖与庇护者。","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"他们会在严苛的法令与贵族的反复无常之间被翻搅，蹂躏，直到......忍无可忍。","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"但即使您活着，那一切流血、暴力与动乱，也迟早会发生。","id":290},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我说得对吗，老师？","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沃里克伯爵","text":"呵呵......到了那时候，你会如何做？","id":292},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我会......伸手将他们从灰烬中拉起来。","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"......","id":294},{"type":"Dialog","id":295},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":296},{"type":"Text","text":"老师失去血色的脸上，不知为何浮现了欣慰的笑容。","id":297},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沃里克伯爵","text":"贪婪的德拉克，野心无穷无尽的德拉克......我半生的搜寻，没有找错......呼......","id":298},{"type":"Text","text":"他摘下眼镜，缓慢而艰难地转头，望向大雪纷飞的窗外。","id":299},{"type":"Text","text":"十年前的冬夜，他念完传奇小说，手指抚过书脊上烫金的塔拉字母时，也曾露出那样眷恋又期盼的眼神。","id":300},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沃里克伯爵","text":"我看到......属于塔拉的新时代......近在眼前。","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沃里克伯爵","text":"可是......","id":302},{"type":"multiline","name":"沃里克伯爵","delay":"0.02","text":"拉芙希妮啊......","id":303},{"type":"multiline","name":"沃里克伯爵","delay":"0.02","text":"还有......","id":304},{"type":"multiline","name":"沃里克伯爵","end":"true","text":"你......","id":305},{"type":"Text","text":"我一动不动地站在门口。玻璃窗上，映出的是我被冰冷的火焰照亮的脸。","id":306},{"type":"Text","text":"如此惶恐，却与那副怜悯的面孔，一模一样。","id":307},{"type":"Text","text":"......拉芙希妮，你会是谁的学生？","id":308},{"type":"Dialog","id":309},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":310},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":312},{"type":"Character","id":313},{"type":"Image","id":314}],"characters":["菲舍尔","开斯特公爵","受伤的流民","苇草","维恩","塔拉流民","莫兰","爱布拉娜","威灵顿公爵","维多利亚军官","沃里克伯爵","拉芙希妮"]}